flow.mentorSays:
Let's understand what this Multi-Select Checkbox challenge asks for.

**Challenge Description:**
// Given list of items:
const items = [
  { id: 1, name: "Apple" },
  { id: 2, name: "Banana" },
  { id: 3, name: "Orange" }
];

// Requirements:
// - Each item has checkbox
// - "Select All" checkbox at top
// - Show count of selected items
// - "Clear Selection" button
// - Display selected items below

**What we need to build:**
This challenge tests your understanding of Array state, checkbox handling.

**Time estimate:** 15 minutes
**Difficulty level:** Mid

This is a practical interview question that tests your understanding of core Angular concepts and your ability to implement them correctly.

